### Potential Errors
- Broadcast
    - Server disconnects, and client attempts to connect to it, while server doesn't exist
- Host and Join
    - client disconnects ✓
    - Server Disconnects
    - False IP or Port
    - Client opens before server
    - Connection Fails
    - Error when client disconnects ✓